data.meta_description: Prints of An official two-day state visit to the UK by King Bhumibol Adulyadej (Rama IX) (1927)
data.text:
An official two-day state visit to the UK by King Bhumibol Adulyadej (Rama IX) (1927-) and Queen Sirikit (1932-) of Thailand - arriving at Gatwick Airport. Date: 1960. Mary Evans Picture Library makes available wonderful images created for people to enjoy over the centuries. Â© Illustrated London News Ltd/Mary Evans
